  "description": {
    "en": [
      "This Glow in the Dark 130-piece fort set is a made-to-order color-box item. The box shows a 4+ age mark.",
      "The set uses PP plastic rods and connector balls. Children insert and twist the rods to build glowing forts, tents, rockets, houses, and tunnels.",
      "Logo, space-theme artwork, manual, colors, accessory mix, and private-label packing can be adjusted.",
      "No public price is shown. Quotation follows confirmed artwork, configuration, quantity, and packing."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "Glow in the Dark 130件为夜光堡垒拼搭彩盒定制款，盒面标注适用年龄 4 岁以上。",
      "产品采用 PP 塑料杆件和连接球，插入后旋转固定，可搭建夜光城堡、帐篷、火箭、房屋、隧道等造型。",
      "LOGO、太空主题画面、说明书、配色、配件组合和贴牌包装都可以调整。",
      "不公开标价，确认画面、配置、数量和包装后报价。"
    ]
  },
